name: Moto-Elite Bar End Sliders
description:
Due to popular demand and countless e-mails by customers asking for a bar end mirror slider, we decided to design and produce our own.

The bar end sliders are universal and fit any bar end mirrors.  They come with their own installation hardware and are made out of a strong synthetic polymer made to withstand impact and abrasion in case of a tip over or crash.

The hardware is stainless steel and uses an expanding well nut for easy installation and aids in clip on/handlebar vibration relief.

MADE IN THE USA.

(Florida residents, please add 6% sales tax)
Free shipping to anywhere in the U.S.A. on all orders
Shipping charges apply to all other areas of the world.

name: Moto-Elite Folding Bar End Mirrors
description:
Moto-Elite Folding Bar End Mirrors
ME-0001

• Fully foldable with grooved notches & spring loaded ball bearing.
• Billet Aluminum Construction 
• 3" Convex Glass
• Fits 7/8" clip-ons and handlebars
• Rubber O-Rings to prevent vibration
• Universal joint for mounting on either side
• Stainless bolts

$99/pair

Free shipping to anywhere in the U.S.A. on all orders

Made in Japan. Assembled by hand in U.S.A.

name: Moto-Elite Water Bottle
description:
The perfect water bottle for those hot days at the race track.

Easy to squeeze, easy to open, and 100% leak-proof, the Bontrager 24 oz waterbottle features a screw top lid and large opening that makes adding your favorite powdered drink or adding ice a cinch.
